<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jewellery Website Landing Page</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 100vh;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .brand img {
            width: 40px;
        }

        .brand p {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav {
            text-align: right;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .main-background {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .main-content {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .main-content h1 {
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .main-content h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .main-content p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .main-content a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #fff;
            background: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 60px 0;
        }

        .section-head h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section-head p {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .collection-list ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .collection-list ul li {
            width: 30%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .collection-list ul li img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .list-head h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .list-head span {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .new-collection {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 400px;
            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1200x400') no-repeat center center/cover;
        }

        .new-collection .mid-title {
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .new-collection .mid-title h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        .new-collection .mid-title a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #fff;
            background: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .card-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .card-wrapper section {
            width: 48%;
            height: 200px;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .card-title h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card-title p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .gallery {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .gallery ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .gallery ul li {
            width: 32%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .gallery ul li img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .about {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 60px 0;
        }

        .wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .wrapper .left {
            width: 45%;
            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/500x400') no-repeat center center/cover;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .wrapper .right {
            width: 45%;
        }

        .wrapper .text h3 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .wrapper .text p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .contact form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .contact form input,
        .contact form textarea {
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .contact form input[type="button"] {
            width: auto;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .bottom-links {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .bottom-links ul {
            list-style: none;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .bottom-links ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .bottom-links ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer {
            background: #222;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header id="home">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="brand">
                <img src="https://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/joke-battles/images/4/41/Infinity_Logo_Gold.png/revision/latest?cb=20151230235753" alt="Infinity Golden Jewelry">
                <p>Infinity Golden Jewelry</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#custom-sec">Custom Jewelry</a></li>
                <li><a href="#designer-sec">Designer Jewelry</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="main-background">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="main-content">
                    <h1>Infinity Golden Jewelry</h1>
                    <h2>24 Caratage Yellow Gold Bracelet</h2>
                    <p>Shop the latest designs from new brands</p>
                    <a href="#custom-sec">- View Products</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="section" id="custom-sec">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Custom Jewelry</h2>
                <p>Latest Design</p>
            </div>
            <div class="collection-list">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <img src="http://www.thomassabo.com/dw/image/v2/AAQY_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-ts-master-catalog/default/dwbb260100/productimages/LBA0102-415-12.png?sw=310&sfrm=png" alt="Bracelet">
                        <div class="list-head">
                            <h3>Bracelets</h3>
                            <span>The description of the item.</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <img src="https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/27/41/69/274169b4444ccf7448d4133c13dd05c1.png" alt="Ring">
                        <div class="list-head">
                            <h3>Rings</h3>
                            <span>The description of the item.</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <img src="http://pngimg.com/uploads/necklace/necklace_PNG6701.png" alt="Necklace">
                        <div class="list-head">
                            <h3>Necklace</h3>
                            <span>The description of the item.</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="new-collection">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mid-title">
                <h2>New Collections</h2>
                <a href="#">Shop Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="designer-sec">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Designer Jewelry</h2>
                <p>New Arrival</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-wrapper">
                <section>
                    <div class="card-title">
                        <h3>New Collection</h3>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <div class="card-title">
                        <h3>Limited Edition</h3>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="gallery">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Gallery</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="collection-list">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300" alt="Gallery Image 1">
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300" alt="Gallery Image 2">
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300" alt="Gallery Image 3">
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="left"></div>
                <div class="right">
                    <div class="text">
                        <h3>Our Story</h3>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Mauris pellentesque erat in blandit luctus. Pellentesque scelerisque nunc vitae dolor tempor, et dictum turpis faucibus.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact" id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-head">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            </div>
            <form action="#">
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name">
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email">
                <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Message"></textarea>
                <input type="button" value="Send">
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bottom-links">
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#custom-sec">Privacy</a></li>
                <li><a href="#designer-sec">Terms & Conditions</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2023. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
